title: [Honeysuckle Avenue]
description: Nighttime has settled in on the Isle of the Four Winds, and a crisp coolness is in the air.  Accented by silvery moonlight, a small pale yellow-hued boutique appears to have a golden glow to it.  The shadows of the mannequins, lit from behind by the flickering candlelight inside the boutique, move across the street in an eerie dance.

A boutique has been nestled in amongst the various shops along Honeysuckle Avenue.  In contrast to the surrounding shops, the small cottage housing the boutique has been painted a soft yellow with a lighter shade for the trim.  Ladies pause, now and again, to admire the latest fashions modeled by the mannequins in the window.
